{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"As a clergyman,"},{"time":27000,"text":"you can imagine how"},{"time":29000,"text":"out of place I feel."},{"time":31000,"text":"I feel like a fish out of water,"},{"time":34000,"text":"or maybe an owl out of the air."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"I was preaching in San Jose some time ago,"},{"time":43000,"text":"and my friend Mark Kvamme,"},{"time":46000,"text":"who helped introduce me"},{"time":48000,"text":"to this conference,"},{"time":51000,"text":"brought several CEOs"},{"time":53000,"text":"and leaders"},{"time":56000,"text":"of some of the companies here in the Silicon Valley"},{"time":59000,"text":"to have breakfast with me, or I with them."},{"time":63000,"text":"And I was so stimulated."},{"time":66000,"text":"And had such -- it was an"},{"time":68000,"text":"eye-opening experience"},{"time":72000,"text":"to hear them talk about"},{"time":74000,"text":"the world that is yet to come"},{"time":78000,"text":"through technology"},{"time":80000,"text":"and science."},{"time":83000,"text":"I know that we're near the end of this conference,"},{"time":87000,"text":"and some of you may be wondering"},{"time":89000,"text":"why they have a speaker"},{"time":91000,"text":"from the field of religion."},{"time":96000,"text":"Richard can answer that,"},{"time":98000,"text":"because he made that decision."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"But some years ago I was on an elevator in Philadelphia,"},{"time":103000,"text":"coming down."},{"time":105000,"text":"I was to address a conference"},{"time":107000,"text":"at a hotel."},{"time":109000,"text":"And on that elevator a man said,"},{"time":111000,"text":"\"I hear Billy Graham is staying in this hotel.\""},{"time":114000,"text":"And another man looked in my direction and said,"},{"time":117000,"text":"\"Yes, there he is. He's on this elevator with us.\""},{"time":120000,"text":"And this man looked me up and down"},{"time":122000,"text":"for about 10 seconds,"},{"time":124000,"text":"and he said, \"My, what an anticlimax!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"I hope"},{"time":135000,"text":"that you won't feel that these few moments with me"},{"time":137000,"text":"is not a -- is an anticlimax,"},{"time":140000,"text":"after all these tremendous"},{"time":142000,"text":"talks that you've heard,"},{"time":145000,"text":"and addresses, which I intend to listen to every one of them."},{"time":148000,"text":"But I was"},{"time":151000,"text":"on an airplane in the east some years ago,"},{"time":155000,"text":"and the man sitting across the aisle from me"},{"time":158000,"text":"was the mayor of Charlotte, North Carolina."},{"time":160000,"text":"His name was John Belk. Some of you will probably know him."},{"time":164000,"text":"And there was a drunk man on there,"},{"time":166000,"text":"and he got up out of his seat two or three times,"},{"time":168000,"text":"and he was making everybody upset"},{"time":170000,"text":"by what he was trying to do."},{"time":172000,"text":"And he was slapping the stewardess"},{"time":174000,"text":"and pinching her as she went by,"},{"time":177000,"text":"and everybody was upset with him."},{"time":181000,"text":"And finally, John Belk said,"},{"time":183000,"text":"\"Do you know who's sitting here?\""},{"time":186000,"text":"And the man said, \"No, who?\""},{"time":188000,"text":"He said, \"It's Billy Graham,"},{"time":190000,"text":"the preacher.\""},{"time":192000,"text":"He said, \"You don't say!\""},{"time":194000,"text":"And he turned to me, and he said, \"Put her there!\""},{"time":197000,"text":"He said, \"Your sermons have certainly helped me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":208000,"text":"And I suppose that that's true"},{"time":210000,"text":"with thousands of people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":219000,"text":"I know that as you have been peering into the future,"},{"time":223000,"text":"and as we've heard some of it here tonight,"},{"time":227000,"text":"I would like to live in that age"},{"time":230000,"text":"and see what is going to be."},{"time":233000,"text":"But I won't,"},{"time":235000,"text":"because I'm 80 years old. This is my eightieth year,"},{"time":238000,"text":"and I know that my time is brief."},{"time":243000,"text":"I have phlebitis at the moment, in both legs,"},{"time":246000,"text":"and that's the reason that I had to have a little help in getting up here,"},{"time":249000,"text":"because I have Parkinson's disease"},{"time":250000,"text":"in addition to that,"},{"time":252000,"text":"and some other problems that I won't talk about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":257000,"text":"But this is not the first time"},{"time":259000,"text":"that we've had a technological revolution."},{"time":264000,"text":"We've had others."},{"time":266000,"text":"And there's one that I want to talk about."},{"time":270000,"text":"In one generation,"},{"time":272000,"text":"the nation of the people of Israel"},{"time":275000,"text":"had a tremendous and dramatic change"},{"time":279000,"text":"that made them a great power in the Near East."},{"time":283000,"text":"A man by the name of David"},{"time":285000,"text":"came to the throne,"},{"time":287000,"text":"and King David became one of the great leaders"},{"time":290000,"text":"of his generation."},{"time":295000,"text":"He was a man of tremendous leadership."},{"time":298000,"text":"He had the favor of God with him."},{"time":301000,"text":"He was a brilliant poet,"},{"time":305000,"text":"philosopher, writer, soldier --"},{"time":309000,"text":"with strategies in battle and conflict"},{"time":312000,"text":"that people study even today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315000,"text":"But about two centuries before David,"},{"time":319000,"text":"the Hittites"},{"time":321000,"text":"had discovered the secret"},{"time":323000,"text":"of smelting and processing of iron,"},{"time":327000,"text":"and, slowly, that skill spread."},{"time":329000,"text":"But they wouldn't allow the Israelis"},{"time":332000,"text":"to look into it, or to have any."},{"time":336000,"text":"But David changed all of that,"},{"time":338000,"text":"and he introduced the Iron Age"},{"time":340000,"text":"to Israel."},{"time":342000,"text":"And the Bible says that David laid up great stores of iron,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and which archaeologists have found,"},{"time":348000,"text":"that in present-day Palestine,"},{"time":350000,"text":"there are evidences of that generation."},{"time":354000,"text":"Now, instead of crude tools"},{"time":357000,"text":"made of sticks and stones,"},{"time":360000,"text":"Israel now had iron plows,"},{"time":363000,"text":"and sickles, and hoes"},{"time":365000,"text":"and military weapons."},{"time":368000,"text":"And in the course of one generation,"},{"time":371000,"text":"Israel was completely changed."},{"time":374000,"text":"The introduction of iron, in some ways,"},{"time":377000,"text":"had an impact"},{"time":380000,"text":"a little bit like the microchip"},{"time":382000,"text":"has had on our generation."},{"time":389000,"text":"And"},{"time":391000,"text":"David found"},{"time":393000,"text":"that there were many problems that technology could not solve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397000,"text":"There were many problems still left."},{"time":402000,"text":"And they're still with us, and you haven't solved them,"},{"time":405000,"text":"and I haven't heard anybody here speak to that."},{"time":409000,"text":"How do we solve these three problems"},{"time":411000,"text":"that I'd like to mention?"},{"time":414000,"text":"The first one that David saw"},{"time":416000,"text":"was human evil."},{"time":418000,"text":"Where does it come from?"},{"time":421000,"text":"How do we solve it?"},{"time":423000,"text":"Over again and again"},{"time":425000,"text":"in the Psalms,"},{"time":427000,"text":"which Gladstone said was the greatest book in the world,"},{"time":432000,"text":"David describes the evils of the human race."},{"time":435000,"text":"And yet he says,"},{"time":437000,"text":"\"He restores my soul.\""},{"time":440000,"text":"Have you ever thought about what a contradiction we are?"},{"time":443000,"text":"On one hand, we can probe the deepest secrets of the universe"},{"time":447000,"text":"and dramatically push back the frontiers of technology,"},{"time":451000,"text":"as this conference vividly demonstrates."},{"time":456000,"text":"We've seen under the sea,"},{"time":458000,"text":"three miles down,"},{"time":460000,"text":"or galaxies hundreds of billions of years"},{"time":463000,"text":"out in the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466000,"text":"But on the other hand,"},{"time":469000,"text":"something is wrong."},{"time":473000,"text":"Our battleships,"},{"time":475000,"text":"our soldiers,"},{"time":477000,"text":"are on a frontier now,"},{"time":479000,"text":"almost ready to go to war"},{"time":481000,"text":"with Iraq."},{"time":483000,"text":"Now, what causes this?"},{"time":485000,"text":"Why do we have these wars in every generation,"},{"time":488000,"text":"and in every part of the world?"},{"time":491000,"text":"And revolutions?"},{"time":494000,"text":"We can't get along with other people,"},{"time":496000,"text":"even in our own families."},{"time":498000,"text":"We find ourselves in the paralyzing grip"},{"time":500000,"text":"of self-destructive habits we can't break."},{"time":504000,"text":"Racism and injustice and violence sweep our world,"},{"time":507000,"text":"bringing a tragic harvest of heartache and death."},{"time":513000,"text":"Even the most sophisticated among us"},{"time":515000,"text":"seem powerless to break this cycle."},{"time":518000,"text":"I would like to see Oracle"},{"time":520000,"text":"take up that,"},{"time":523000,"text":"or"},{"time":526000,"text":"some other"},{"time":528000,"text":"technological geniuses work on this."},{"time":532000,"text":"How do we change man,"},{"time":536000,"text":"so that he doesn't lie and cheat,"},{"time":538000,"text":"and our newspapers are not filled with stories"},{"time":541000,"text":"of fraud in business or labor"},{"time":543000,"text":"or athletics or wherever?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548000,"text":"The Bible says the problem is within us,"},{"time":552000,"text":"within our hearts and our souls."},{"time":555000,"text":"Our problem is that we are separated"},{"time":557000,"text":"from our Creator,"},{"time":560000,"text":"which we call God,"},{"time":562000,"text":"and we need to have our souls restored,"},{"time":567000,"text":"something only God can do."},{"time":569000,"text":"Jesus said, \"For out of the heart"},{"time":571000,"text":"come evil thoughts:"},{"time":573000,"text":"murders, sexual immorality,"},{"time":576000,"text":"theft, false testimonies,"},{"time":579000,"text":"slander.\""},{"time":581000,"text":"The British philosopher Bertrand Russell"},{"time":583000,"text":"was not a religious man,"},{"time":586000,"text":"but he said, \"It's in our hearts that the evil lies,"},{"time":589000,"text":"and it's from our hearts"},{"time":591000,"text":"that it must be plucked out.\""},{"time":594000,"text":"Albert Einstein --"},{"time":596000,"text":"I was just talking to someone, when I was speaking at Princeton,"},{"time":599000,"text":"and I met"},{"time":601000,"text":"Mr. Einstein."},{"time":603000,"text":"He didn't have a doctor's degree, because he said"},{"time":605000,"text":"nobody was qualified to give him one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":607000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":611000,"text":"But he made this statement."},{"time":613000,"text":"He said, \"It's easier to denature plutonium"},{"time":616000,"text":"than to denature the evil spirit of man.\""},{"time":619000,"text":"And many of you, I'm sure,"},{"time":621000,"text":"have thought about that"},{"time":623000,"text":"and puzzled over it."},{"time":625000,"text":"You've seen people"},{"time":627000,"text":"take beneficial technological advances,"},{"time":630000,"text":"such as the Internet we've heard about tonight,"},{"time":632000,"text":"and twist them into something corrupting."},{"time":636000,"text":"You've seen brilliant people devise computer viruses"},{"time":639000,"text":"that bring down whole systems."},{"time":642000,"text":"The Oklahoma City bombing was simple technology,"},{"time":645000,"text":"horribly used."},{"time":648000,"text":"The problem is not technology."},{"time":650000,"text":"The problem is the person or persons using it."},{"time":655000,"text":"King David said"},{"time":657000,"text":"that he knew the depths of his own soul."},{"time":660000,"text":"He couldn't free himself from personal problems"},{"time":663000,"text":"and personal evils"},{"time":666000,"text":"that included murder and adultery."},{"time":669000,"text":"Yet King David sought God's forgiveness,"},{"time":671000,"text":"and said, \"You can restore my soul.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":674000,"text":"You see, the Bible teaches"},{"time":677000,"text":"that we're more than a body and a mind."},{"time":681000,"text":"We are a soul."},{"time":684000,"text":"And there's something inside of us"},{"time":687000,"text":"that is beyond our understanding."},{"time":690000,"text":"That's the part of us that yearns"},{"time":693000,"text":"for God, or something more"},{"time":696000,"text":"than we find in technology."},{"time":699000,"text":"Your soul is that part of you that"},{"time":701000,"text":"yearns for meaning in life,"},{"time":703000,"text":"and which seeks for something beyond this life."},{"time":706000,"text":"It's the part of you that yearns, really, for God."},{"time":708000,"text":"I find [that] young people all over the world"},{"time":710000,"text":"are searching for something."},{"time":713000,"text":"They don't know what it is. I speak at many universities,"},{"time":716000,"text":"and I have many questions and answer periods, and"},{"time":719000,"text":"whether it's Cambridge, or Harvard,"},{"time":721000,"text":"or Oxford --"},{"time":723000,"text":"I've spoken at all of those universities."},{"time":725000,"text":"I'm going to Harvard in about three or four --"},{"time":727000,"text":"no, it's about two months from now --"},{"time":729000,"text":"to give a lecture."},{"time":731000,"text":"And I'll be asked the same questions that I was asked"},{"time":733000,"text":"the last few times I've been there."},{"time":736000,"text":"And it'll be on"},{"time":738000,"text":"these questions:"},{"time":740000,"text":"where did I come from? Why am I here? Where am I going?"},{"time":743000,"text":"What's life all about? Why am I here?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":747000,"text":"Even if you have no religious belief,"},{"time":749000,"text":"there are times when you wonder that there's something else."},{"time":752000,"text":"Thomas Edison also said,"},{"time":755000,"text":"\"When you see everything that happens in the world of science,"},{"time":758000,"text":"and in the working of the universe,"},{"time":760000,"text":"you cannot deny that there's a captain on the bridge.\""},{"time":764000,"text":"I remember once,"},{"time":766000,"text":"I sat beside Mrs. Gorbachev"},{"time":768000,"text":"at a White House dinner."},{"time":771000,"text":"I went to Ambassador Dobrynin, whom I knew very well."},{"time":773000,"text":"And I'd been to Russia several times under the Communists,"},{"time":777000,"text":"and they'd given me marvelous freedom that I didn't expect."},{"time":783000,"text":"And I knew Mr. Dobrynin very well,"},{"time":785000,"text":"and I said,"},{"time":787000,"text":"\"I'm going to sit beside Mrs. Gorbachev tonight."},{"time":790000,"text":"What shall I talk to her about?\""},{"time":792000,"text":"And he surprised me with the answer."},{"time":794000,"text":"He said, \"Talk to her about religion and philosophy."},{"time":797000,"text":"That's what she's really interested in.\""},{"time":800000,"text":"I was a little bit surprised, but that evening"},{"time":803000,"text":"that's what we talked about,"},{"time":805000,"text":"and it was a stimulating conversation."},{"time":807000,"text":"And afterward, she said,"},{"time":809000,"text":"\"You know, I'm an atheist,"},{"time":811000,"text":"but I know that there's something up there"},{"time":813000,"text":"higher than we are.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":816000,"text":"The second problem"},{"time":818000,"text":"that King David realized he could not solve"},{"time":822000,"text":"was the problem of human suffering."},{"time":824000,"text":"Writing the oldest book in the world was Job,"},{"time":827000,"text":"and he said,"},{"time":829000,"text":"\"Man is born unto trouble as the sparks fly upward.\""},{"time":833000,"text":"Yes, to be sure, science has done much to push back"},{"time":836000,"text":"certain types of human suffering."},{"time":839000,"text":"But I'm --"},{"time":841000,"text":"in a few months, I'll be 80 years of age."},{"time":844000,"text":"I admit that I'm very grateful"},{"time":846000,"text":"for all the medical advances"},{"time":848000,"text":"that have kept me in relatively good health"},{"time":850000,"text":"all these years."},{"time":852000,"text":"My doctors at the Mayo Clinic urged me"},{"time":854000,"text":"not to take this trip out here to this -- to be here."},{"time":858000,"text":"I haven't given a talk in nearly four months."},{"time":863000,"text":"And when you speak as much as I do,"},{"time":865000,"text":"three or four times a day,"},{"time":867000,"text":"you get rusty."},{"time":869000,"text":"That's the reason I'm using this podium"},{"time":871000,"text":"and using these notes."},{"time":874000,"text":"Every time you ever hear me on the television or somewhere,"},{"time":877000,"text":"I'm ad-libbing."},{"time":879000,"text":"I'm not reading. I never read an address."},{"time":883000,"text":"I never read a speech or a talk or a lecture."},{"time":887000,"text":"I talk ad lib."},{"time":889000,"text":"But tonight, I've"},{"time":891000,"text":"got some notes here so that if"},{"time":893000,"text":"I begin to forget,"},{"time":895000,"text":"which I do sometimes,"},{"time":898000,"text":"I've got something I can turn to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":901000,"text":"But even here among us,"},{"time":905000,"text":"most --"},{"time":909000,"text":"in the most advanced society in the world,"},{"time":912000,"text":"we have poverty."},{"time":914000,"text":"We have families that self-destruct,"},{"time":917000,"text":"friends that betray us."},{"time":919000,"text":"Unbearable psychological pressures bear down on us."},{"time":922000,"text":"I've never met a person in the world"},{"time":924000,"text":"that didn't have a problem"},{"time":926000,"text":"or a worry."},{"time":928000,"text":"Why do we suffer? It's an age-old question"},{"time":931000,"text":"that we haven't answered."},{"time":933000,"text":"Yet David again and again said"},{"time":937000,"text":"that he would turn to God."},{"time":940000,"text":"He said, \"The Lord is my shepherd.\""},{"time":944000,"text":"The final problem that David knew he could not solve"},{"time":948000,"text":"was death."},{"time":951000,"text":"Many commentators have said that death"},{"time":953000,"text":"is the forbidden subject of our generation."},{"time":956000,"text":"Most people live as if"},{"time":959000,"text":"they're never going to die."},{"time":961000,"text":"Technology projects the myth"},{"time":964000,"text":"of control over our mortality."},{"time":968000,"text":"We see people on our screens."},{"time":970000,"text":"Marilyn Monroe is just as beautiful on the screen"},{"time":972000,"text":"as she was in person,"},{"time":974000,"text":"and our -- many young people think she's still alive."},{"time":978000,"text":"They don't know that she's dead."},{"time":980000,"text":"Or Clark Gable, or whoever it is."},{"time":982000,"text":"The old stars, they come to life."},{"time":986000,"text":"And they're --"},{"time":989000,"text":"they're just as great on that screen as they were in person."},{"time":994000,"text":"But death is inevitable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996000,"text":"I spoke some time ago to"},{"time":999000,"text":"a joint session of Congress, last year."},{"time":1003000,"text":"And we were meeting in that room,"},{"time":1006000,"text":"the statue room."},{"time":1008000,"text":"About 300 of them were there."},{"time":1011000,"text":"And I said, \"There's one thing that we have in common in this room,"},{"time":1015000,"text":"all of us together, whether Republican or Democrat,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"or whoever.\""},{"time":1020000,"text":"I said, \"We're all going to die."},{"time":1022000,"text":"And we have that in common with all these great men of the past"},{"time":1025000,"text":"that are staring down at us.\""},{"time":1029000,"text":"And it's often difficult for young people"},{"time":1031000,"text":"to understand that."},{"time":1034000,"text":"It's difficult for them to understand that they're going to die."},{"time":1038000,"text":"As the ancient writer of Ecclesiastes wrote,"},{"time":1042000,"text":"he said, there's every activity under heaven."},{"time":1046000,"text":"There's a time to be born,"},{"time":1049000,"text":"and there's a time to die."},{"time":1051000,"text":"I've stood at the deathbed"},{"time":1054000,"text":"of several famous people,"},{"time":1056000,"text":"whom you would know."},{"time":1058000,"text":"I've talked to them."},{"time":1060000,"text":"I've seen them in those agonizing moments"},{"time":1062000,"text":"when they were scared to death."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1065000,"text":"And yet, a few years earlier,"},{"time":1069000,"text":"death never crossed their mind."},{"time":1071000,"text":"I talked to a woman this past week"},{"time":1075000,"text":"whose father"},{"time":1078000,"text":"was a famous doctor."},{"time":1081000,"text":"She said he never thought of God, never talked about God,"},{"time":1084000,"text":"didn't believe in God. He was an atheist."},{"time":1089000,"text":"But she said,"},{"time":1091000,"text":"as he came to die,"},{"time":1093000,"text":"he sat up on the side of the bed one day,"},{"time":1097000,"text":"and he asked the nurse if he could see the chaplain."},{"time":1100000,"text":"And he said, for the first time in his life"},{"time":1102000,"text":"he'd thought about the inevitable,"},{"time":1107000,"text":"and about God."},{"time":1109000,"text":"Was there a God?"},{"time":1113000,"text":"A few years ago, a university student asked me,"},{"time":1117000,"text":"\"What is the greatest surprise in your life?\""},{"time":1120000,"text":"And I said, \"The greatest surprise in my life"},{"time":1122000,"text":"is the brevity of life."},{"time":1125000,"text":"It passes so fast.\""},{"time":1130000,"text":"But it does not need to have to be that way."},{"time":1132000,"text":"Wernher von Braun,"},{"time":1135000,"text":"in the aftermath of World War II concluded, quote:"},{"time":1138000,"text":"\"science and religion are not antagonists."},{"time":1141000,"text":"On the contrary, they're sisters.\""},{"time":1145000,"text":"He put it on a personal basis."},{"time":1147000,"text":"I knew Dr. von Braun very well."},{"time":1150000,"text":"And he said, \"Speaking for myself,"},{"time":1152000,"text":"I can only say that the grandeur of the cosmos"},{"time":1155000,"text":"serves only to confirm"},{"time":1157000,"text":"a belief in the certainty of a creator.\""},{"time":1160000,"text":"He also said,"},{"time":1162000,"text":"\"In our search to know God,"},{"time":1164000,"text":"I've come to believe that the life of Jesus Christ"},{"time":1168000,"text":"should be the focus of our efforts and inspiration."},{"time":1172000,"text":"The reality of this life and His resurrection"},{"time":1174000,"text":"is the hope of mankind.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1177000,"text":"I've done a lot of speaking in Germany"},{"time":1179000,"text":"and in France, and in different parts of the world --"},{"time":1182000,"text":"105 countries it's been my privilege to speak in."},{"time":1187000,"text":"And I was invited one day to visit"},{"time":1191000,"text":"Chancellor Adenauer,"},{"time":1193000,"text":"who was looked upon as sort of the founder of modern Germany,"},{"time":1198000,"text":"since the war."},{"time":1200000,"text":"And he once -- and he said to me,"},{"time":1202000,"text":"he said, \"Young man.\" He said,"},{"time":1204000,"text":"\"Do you believe in the resurrection of Jesus Christ?\""},{"time":1208000,"text":"And I said, \"Sir, I do.\""},{"time":1210000,"text":"He said, \"So do I.\""},{"time":1212000,"text":"He said, \"When I leave office,"},{"time":1214000,"text":"I'm going to spend my time writing a book"},{"time":1217000,"text":"on why Jesus Christ rose again,"},{"time":1220000,"text":"and why it's so important to believe that.\""},{"time":1226000,"text":"In one of his plays,"},{"time":1228000,"text":"Alexander Solzhenitsyn"},{"time":1231000,"text":"depicts a man dying,"},{"time":1233000,"text":"who says to those gathered around his bed,"},{"time":1236000,"text":"\"The moment when it's terrible to feel regret"},{"time":1238000,"text":"is when one is dying.\""},{"time":1241000,"text":"How should one live in order not to feel regret when one is dying?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1246000,"text":"Blaise Pascal"},{"time":1248000,"text":"asked exactly that question"},{"time":1250000,"text":"in seventeenth-century France."},{"time":1252000,"text":"Pascal has been called the architect"},{"time":1254000,"text":"of modern civilization."},{"time":1257000,"text":"He was a brilliant scientist"},{"time":1259000,"text":"at the frontiers of mathematics,"},{"time":1261000,"text":"even as a teenager."},{"time":1264000,"text":"He is viewed by many as the founder of the probability theory,"},{"time":1268000,"text":"and a creator of the first model of a computer."},{"time":1272000,"text":"And of course, you are all familiar with"},{"time":1274000,"text":"the computer language named for him."},{"time":1277000,"text":"Pascal explored in depth our human dilemmas"},{"time":1279000,"text":"of evil, suffering and death."},{"time":1283000,"text":"He was astounded"},{"time":1286000,"text":"at the phenomenon we've been considering:"},{"time":1289000,"text":"that people can achieve extraordinary heights"},{"time":1291000,"text":"in science, the arts and human enterprise,"},{"time":1294000,"text":"yet they also are full of anger, hypocrisy"},{"time":1297000,"text":"and have -- and self-hatreds."},{"time":1301000,"text":"Pascal saw us as a remarkable mixture"},{"time":1303000,"text":"of genius and self-delusion."},{"time":1306000,"text":"On November 23,"},{"time":1308000,"text":"1654,"},{"time":1311000,"text":"Pascal had a profound religious experience."},{"time":1315000,"text":"He wrote in his journal these words:"},{"time":1318000,"text":"\"I submit myself,"},{"time":1320000,"text":"absolutely,"},{"time":1323000,"text":"to Jesus Christ, my redeemer.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1326000,"text":"A French historian said,"},{"time":1328000,"text":"two centuries later,"},{"time":1331000,"text":"\"Seldom has so mighty an intellect"},{"time":1334000,"text":"submitted with such humility"},{"time":1337000,"text":"to the authority of Jesus Christ.\""},{"time":1341000,"text":"Pascal came to believe not only the love and the grace of God"},{"time":1344000,"text":"could bring us back into harmony,"},{"time":1349000,"text":"but he believed"},{"time":1351000,"text":"that his own sins and failures could be forgiven,"},{"time":1354000,"text":"and that when he died he would go to a place called heaven."},{"time":1359000,"text":"He experienced it in a way that went beyond"},{"time":1361000,"text":"scientific observation and reason."},{"time":1363000,"text":"It was he who penned the well-known words,"},{"time":1366000,"text":"\"The heart has its reasons,"},{"time":1369000,"text":"which reason knows not of.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1372000,"text":"Equally well known is Pascal's Wager."},{"time":1375000,"text":"Essentially, he said this: \"if you bet on God,"},{"time":1379000,"text":"and open yourself to his love,"},{"time":1381000,"text":"you lose nothing, even if you're wrong."},{"time":1384000,"text":"But if instead you bet that there is no God,"},{"time":1388000,"text":"then you can lose it all, in this life and the life to come.\""},{"time":1393000,"text":"For Pascal, scientific knowledge"},{"time":1395000,"text":"paled beside the knowledge of God."},{"time":1399000,"text":"The knowledge of God was far beyond"},{"time":1401000,"text":"anything that ever crossed his mind."},{"time":1404000,"text":"He was ready to face him"},{"time":1406000,"text":"when he died at the age of 39."},{"time":1409000,"text":"King David lived to be 70,"},{"time":1411000,"text":"a long time in his era."},{"time":1414000,"text":"Yet he too had to face death,"},{"time":1417000,"text":"and he wrote these words:"},{"time":1419000,"text":"\"even though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death,"},{"time":1423000,"text":"I will fear no evil,"},{"time":1425000,"text":"for you are with me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1427000,"text":"This was David's answer to three dilemmas"},{"time":1430000,"text":"of evil, suffering and death."},{"time":1433000,"text":"It can be yours, as well,"},{"time":1437000,"text":"as you seek the living God"},{"time":1439000,"text":"and allow him to fill your life"},{"time":1441000,"text":"and give you hope for the future."},{"time":1446000,"text":"When I was 17 years of age,"},{"time":1450000,"text":"I was born and reared on a farm in North Carolina."},{"time":1454000,"text":"I milked cows every morning, and I had to milk the same cows every evening"},{"time":1456000,"text":"when I came home from school."},{"time":1458000,"text":"And there were 20 of them that I had --"},{"time":1460000,"text":"that I was responsible for,"},{"time":1463000,"text":"and I worked on the farm"},{"time":1466000,"text":"and tried to keep up with my studies."},{"time":1469000,"text":"I didn't make good grades in high school."},{"time":1472000,"text":"I didn't make them in college, until"},{"time":1475000,"text":"something happened in my heart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1477000,"text":"One day, I was faced face-to-face"},{"time":1481000,"text":"with Christ."},{"time":1483000,"text":"He said, \"I am the way, the truth and the life.\""},{"time":1487000,"text":"Can you imagine that? \"I am the truth."},{"time":1490000,"text":"I'm the embodiment of all truth.\""},{"time":1493000,"text":"He was a liar."},{"time":1497000,"text":"Or he was insane."},{"time":1500000,"text":"Or he was what he claimed to be."},{"time":1502000,"text":"Which was he?"},{"time":1504000,"text":"I had to make that decision."},{"time":1506000,"text":"I couldn't prove it."},{"time":1508000,"text":"I couldn't take it to a laboratory"},{"time":1510000,"text":"and experiment with it."},{"time":1512000,"text":"But by faith I said, I believe him,"},{"time":1516000,"text":"and he came into my heart"},{"time":1519000,"text":"and changed my life."},{"time":1521000,"text":"And now I'm ready,"},{"time":1524000,"text":"when I hear that call,"},{"time":1526000,"text":"to go into the presence of God."},{"time":1529000,"text":"Thank you, and God bless all of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1531000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1542000,"text":"Thank you for the privilege. It was great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1544000,"text":"Richard Wurman: You did it."},{"time":1546000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1548000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}